From 027cc1658b3a88e227d378237a233699da057753 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Aaron (via Cowork)" <eggmanaa@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 20:32:14 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix type errors and 5 logic bugs from systematic audit
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Type/compile fixes:
- Add 'population' and 'productionPool' to StatKey (used by worldEvents)
- Remove duplicate selectedAction in GameState
- Centralize Hono AppEnv (Bindings + Variables) in api/types.ts
- Install @cloudflare/workers-types (D1Database was implicit-any)
- Cast unknown c.req.json() and response.json() results across api/hooks/components

Logic fixes:
- actionSystem.ts: income fallback uses ?? not || (respect legit 0 productionIncome)
- actionSystem.ts: refresh stale ACTION UNLOCK PROGRESSION header comment
- worldEvents.ts: remove 3 copy-paste duplicate same-stat effects
  (Rome Pax Romana +3/+3 martial, Mesopotamia -2/-2 martial, Turn 24 +3/+3 martial)
- GameApp.tsx: stop compounding tech bonuses in calculateStats
  (science_bonus_3, science_bonus_5, faith_to_science were re-applying
   to accumulating totals every render — now applied once at tech unlock)
- GameApp.tsx: same-stat event effects now accumulate instead of overwrite
  (fixed in globalEffects, choice.effects, and civEvent.effects loops —
   Gaul's two martial effects now correctly stack to +5 instead of +3)

Verification: npx tsc --noEmit is clean; vite build succeeds.
